data.title: Anti-VMO1 antibody (ab126510)
data.meta_description: Rabbit Polyclonal VMO1 antibody. Suitable for IHC-P and reacts with Human samples.  Immunogen corresponding to Recombinant Fragment Protein within Human VMO1 aa 1-150.
